- Yeah, two pages.

03:56.314 --> 03:57.660
Is that good?

03:57.692 --> 03:58.909
Hmm.

03:59.998 --> 04:03.618
- How 'bout you?
- Ah, we got two perch.

04:04.771 --> 04:08.519
- Is that good?
- Ah, yesterday we had 24, so...

04:11.850 --> 04:15.501
Well, you ain't writing
and the fish ain't biting.

04:17.231 --> 04:19.505
- Ah, no.
- Come on.

04:21.779 --> 04:23.798
Good for ya.

04:25.975 --> 04:27.513
See ya.

05:31.193 --> 05:32.442
Hmm.

05:41.090 --> 05:42.884
- Hi.
- Hi.

05:42.916 --> 05:45.480
I was just thinking about you.

05:45.511 --> 05:46.985
You coming home soon?

05:47.017 --> 05:50.508
Uh, no, I'm just... I'm not finished yet.

05:50.540 --> 05:51.918
Oh.

05:52.654 --> 05:54.000
Okay.

05:54.737 --> 05:56.562
How is it going?

05:56.594 --> 05:58.484
Well, I'm not getting anywhere.

06:01.014 --> 06:03.769
Tomas, don't lose faith.
You have it in you, you know that.

06:03.801 --> 06:05.915
Will you stop saying that?

06:05.948 --> 06:07.805
It's, it's not that simple.

06:11.585 --> 06:16.422
And listen, I was, I was thinking
about what we discussed yesterday.

06:16.454 --> 06:19.081
Do we have to talk about it on the phone?

06:21.708 --> 06:23.212
I might just as well tell you now.

06:23.245 --> 06:24.462
I'm, uh...

06:25.584 --> 06:27.601
I'm not ready for all that.

06:43.041 --> 06:44.899
Keep goin', keep goin'.

06:46.981 --> 06:48.839
We're closed.

